Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.100
 Every week, three ninjas are slain inadvertently on our roads. 

00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:08.060
 This can be avoided. 

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:13.460
 I am Frederick Fahrvergnügen, President of the Royal Association 

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:16.040
 For the Prevention of Accidents involving Nerves 

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:18.940
 Or RSPAIN shortened. (tn: RSPAIN sounds like ass pain) 

00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:21.400
 Did you know that in a recent study, 

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:24.840
 has less than 1% of drivers claimed to have ever seen a ninja? 

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:26.580
 It fits. (Have seen a ninja) (Never seen a ninja) (Said we should fuck off from their passenger seat) 

00:00:26.580 --> 00:00:30.840
 So, in the coming days, we will send these free luminescent headbands 

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:33.780
 to dojoer throughout the country. 

00:00:33.780 --> 00:00:37.960
 If you combine one with a reflective vest, you can be sure to be overlooked. 

00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:40.740
 What else can you do to be a safe ninja in traffic? 

00:00:40.740 --> 00:00:45.100
 Well, you should consider not wearing so much dark clothing. 

00:00:45.100 --> 00:00:47.020
 Barry here is a road safety ninja 

00:00:47.020 --> 00:00:48.220
