00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:55.560
 Why not buy one of our special flashing Ninja Lamps 

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.520
 which can be attached to the belt? 

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:59.980
 Along with our patent-pending Ninja AdSense alarm. 

00:00:59.980 --> 00:01:01.440
 [Beep] 

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:04.380
